query:
SELECT 
  id,
  emailType,
  recipientEmail,
  status,
  errorMessage,
  sentAt
FROM email_logs
WHERE tenant = 'launchbase'
  AND status = 'failed'
  AND sentAt >= DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 24 HOUR)
ORDER BY sentAt DESC
LIMIT 20;
